        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(a) $\\alpha _ { n }$ minimizes $f ( \\mathbf { x } _ { n } + \\alpha \\mathbf { p } _ { n } )$ for all $\\alpha \\in \\mathbb { R }$ where ",
        "bbox": [
            223,
            513,
